solution:
Let $F$ be a point on $\overline{AC}$ such that $\overline{DF}$ is parallel to $\overline{BE}$. Let $BT = 4x$ and $ET=x$.

[asy]
pair A,B,C,D,I,T,F;
A=(0,0);
B=(6,8);
C=(11,0);
D=(9.33,2.66);
